{"type":"message","id":"967fd650","parentId":"e298b118","timestamp":"2026-04-24T00:01:26.994Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating MACD calculations**\n\nI’m thinking we might have enough data without needing the MACD right now. Maybe I could try again by using a smaller dataset, like previously cached historical data if it’s available. It might be a network glitch causing issues, so I’ll plan to rerun the calculations with a script for small retries. I really want to make sure I get the results right!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eab2ccacc4819ab9ea0571cc0c686b\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp6rLPVbTSCiQIpJmeI9qFDmMBi6fsXNS_h_PWgB2WNQ-VaKoacywYu2yI1i4OA_VLJ8jizS1A0t1okIADins3egat9yH5URdYGlUBiA0P6k75ECb70BOLYd6XhWX7ZQ_hmJblN8EsS1iVB1UA0HUso5nJpcG1JZMLvXHTn1XvM6mgqWkWaFZSB4tElDfvQX7bySnMyhHvUsUpZwmvq2ONYi97Wgleq9eklPT3b21z-B_iFrVhgNV7EJhuwZPQG11hu7Ma4HR-LaWYZJcPd7EMFpDTKyPibO52i_I1DFrxGuhFeGzkAQWlQYi7-5XZWLdlsCX_gqh7IB8WxORHZ3mS82oHHIxmsIaVg5W7Qa6ZjoStvb2ds-1l8E-Jtg7w7EG8EgqmCXx-hXOZ-_z1eOR3-O9E6x5QLNdk3ZG3bHiLt2Skf7aVdVEYb7NwgHyW3kt_7ze9q0wo1MdoBoCSV4t9WDHfyXGj3ATp4CsN_4R_EzYE593r1GKi2zaXYAYCyW7Fehsx-XOgychY84ydpRQN-uKorKV168w5unnuTMq9twC7SGSQPBQ7ZZ3BiHtv8Gp-DewlkljGkWdOYfapY_wf6cRGkRZ96VoCinUcgEys0q4TxGpSHdLoS04Sveo4Ra24yYl0FmB70UnBKKWImiJvrZt9CZx5H9yuoiYAzy2KySmwFvb8ZRv_MyDKD8vW6Eu1cJ5Vx-eNGgG3udSluoT6dWGC2eH_Uzy0ACwp_JGNIIHLF6RWarpJ2_gOZecFFHG74VCqjF-_ze6AlaKhEh6tkGc4s2Dn3XE6gaK1oDlXw6zU-8tCGf6PUZEH4hsp2xx8a2sX-XxibSgCL4uw-ROY8LIH6M9iSvZ8GarJIeWLxTIx0hQI508Xse78z_40laIgUgckM3JakKFPhgtWOtDFdhIBlfsAQRHywH2XXyP62omrq2GZZyMO5i6wgn-XF83iGqj-WN42fDGoEYOAeuesEdEef5Dt4sp-RAY_87x9gQflmN7G9wl1dUiCf8ItKOUThWt9mOCyNyBgM0dsArv_NNRfwymtMu86zsrBQGQfxI-wdGCSnkZhBt5aYPkSErxWn5g5MD6CzrPSKzkYvAlMAMmlexIH2Wt6HS3wK9a0GBDhvqQnR0BSMyU092RL-3rzjNxISitbovEhJ7_bFTAJpywwnEw22GEw5UmiOhjOGp0zJiwIT5XKmWfFAet1kCjcQA5wKo2b3ZHpqveKScOk-Pxgiw==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Evaluating MACD calculations**\\n\\nI’m thinking we might have enough data without needing the MACD right now. Maybe I could try again by using a smaller dataset, like previously cached historical data if it’s available. It might be a network glitch causing issues, so I’ll plan to rerun the calculations with a script for small retries. I really want to make sure I get the results right!\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_OlxvONYjhB7rlU9ipXkr1okV|fc_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eab2cfdc58819aa407cada5c7362d7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nimport akshare as ak\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nimport json, time\nsymbol='600487'\nend=datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\nstart=(datetime.now()-timedelta(days=500)).strftime('%Y%m%d')\nlast_err=None\nfor i in range(3):\n    try:\n        h=ak.stock_zh_a_hist(symbol=symbol, period='daily', start_date=start, end_date=end, adjust='qfq').copy()\n        break\n    except Exception as e:\n        last_err=e\n        time.sleep(1+i)\nelse:\n    raise last_err\nclose=h['收盘'].astype(float)\nvol=h['成交量'].astype(float)\nchg=close.diff()\ngain=chg.clip(lower=0)\nloss=-chg.clip(upper=0)\nrs=gain.rolling(14).mean()/loss.rolling(14).mean()\nrsi=100-(100/(1+rs))\nema12=close.ewm(span=12, adjust=False).mean()\nema26=close.ewm(span=26, adjust=False).mean()\ndif=ema12-ema26\ndea=dif.ewm(span=9, adjust=False).mean()\nmacd=(dif-dea)*2\nres={\n 'date': str(h.iloc[-1]['日期']),\n 'rsi14': round(float(rsi.iloc[-1]),2),\n 'dif': round(float(dif.iloc[-1]),2),\n 'dea': round(float(dea.iloc[-1]),2),\n 'macd': round(float(macd.iloc[-1]),2),\n 'vol_vs_5': round(float(vol.iloc[-1]/vol.tail(5).mean()),2),\n 'vol_vs_10': round(float(vol.iloc[-1]/vol.tail(10).mean()),2),\n 'vol_vs_20': round(float(vol.iloc[-1]/vol.tail(20).mean()),2),\n}\nprint(json.dumps(res, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":60},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 - <<'PY'\\nimport akshare as ak\\nimport pandas as pd\\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\\nimport json, time\\nsymbol='600487'\\nend=datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\\nstart=(datetime.now()-timedelta(days=500)).strftime('%Y%m%d')\\nlast_err=None\\nfor i in range(3):\\n    try:\\n        h=ak.stock_zh_a_hist(symbol=symbol, period='daily', start_date=start, end_date=end, adjust='qfq').copy()\\n        break\\n    except Exception as e:\\n        last_err=e\\n        time.sleep(1+i)\\nelse:\\n    raise last_err\\nclose=h['收盘'].astype(float)\\nvol=h['成交量'].astype(float)\\nchg=close.diff()\\ngain=chg.clip(lower=0)\\nloss=-chg.clip(upper=0)\\nrs=gain.rolling(14).mean()/loss.rolling(14).mean()\\nrsi=100-(100/(1+rs))\\nema12=close.ewm(span=12, adjust=False).mean()\\nema26=close.ewm(span=26, adjust=False).mean()\\ndif=ema12-ema26\\ndea=dif.ewm(span=9, adjust=False).mean()\\nmacd=(dif-dea)*2\\nres={\\n 'date': str(h.iloc[-1]['日期']),\\n 'rsi14': round(float(rsi.iloc[-1]),2),\\n 'dif': round(float(dif.iloc[-1]),2),\\n 'dea': round(float(dea.iloc[-1]),2),\\n 'macd': round(float(macd.iloc[-1]),2),\\n 'vol_vs_5': round(float(vol.iloc[-1]/vol.tail(5).mean()),2),\\n 'vol_vs_10': round(float(vol.iloc[-1]/vol.tail(10).mean()),2),\\n 'vol_vs_20': round(float(vol.iloc[-1]/vol.tail(20).mean()),2),\\n}\\nprint(json.dumps(res, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\\nPY\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent\",\"timeout\":60}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":45496,"output":549,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47581,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776988866602,"responseId":"resp_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eab2caf0d4819a92b0ac68fb79ecf3"}}
