{"type":"message","id":"e2c61609","parentId":"6a1e2569","timestamp":"2026-04-24T00:11:34.889Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering stock data retrieval**\n\nI need to think about retrying the process, possibly using loops to effectively gather information. Maybe the market close data from the spot will be enough, but I should check if I can use only the most recent output, which just has the latest numbers and percentage change. I also need to individually fetch quotes with retries if needed. Let’s aim for a more robust method to get the historical data as well.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eab51aa0e4819a8d003a63bc4d79d0\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp6rUebC0K-aZqEH7KyHGjXCL7DASUS0C3b_pWIL8uErtqPHvcL1pGr-cmkhJUs9cM2RAgn-lrsGaf89HHdNg6YVxZcEeSXNk5rsZ4GYRMVGVmyMsl8Vq6hp_Rx2I57xQzCcH69puUW1pqASEFvOM07UVX4aiEkVycs0zMCY-PdO7S1ZgbmU09eWq3VrnXMmnQ7lpq2mKp9R0Ew1YYU6MG5sgTfmrvSXtd1_1Pwt7HV9NEcv8aAwHTIvJ2IpkhGGm0XZiVvTA9zANmHgxGBo6tKex0uP2hoc2KrOFkRtYdGGzxYlwm9icvklvVqTrVwoYEOWodXrEnqk_5Dt1HDfwzx4fH_cWbVBbja8p_dufKeugFl2U8kaBA0_uHr7FOQ0H-F17GtYCLI5p3Bkr-f7FdQpsij13w9PqeF7h3bpzTlS4rMm_Xxf83tq7xBwOaxlTxwGoaMU2Y7aa-trBArgm3lPCLAL00lhT6CdobcTuDPxDhb9t1n3qJeyATt-NQLiqvJPXJAcqrQVFXRYUmMm22LVJQbeTUY7PKUgm5ogs_d_I0EDUBaOYJwNtRNtWi6om2caq04DkHyIf79xoQsC78scMBzizRP9yg_tEm8SvVUz4HvZKbt3erU1onm96CZfA2JKTdSUzqLEVuVUPH7kIqd5ZPjRSVsy-wkZIZq30_NqOXFGGwQT7nq08zfSLGi0TO7frckVuqTOZ131gALXUB2th3h46Ge4_Mkl6_gXZX0fmkKmqk2GOPYztaoPRaop8kJ2x_ilXPmOO-lG-eGnBLZMpKL-7G_wmF78Ar0sZ8L4PADPbmg_FtDWabL3VnMl6vNdah8QKssv1JjSsyy2HnoZEvDrHfbd-G5XVHsFVWXn0EjxUHhiLj3IRE_uxuPr1AjOfg-k7-b3e29amHCjBLxipI0isTxiq4LLyOwhoHa8LBghM57TmUf4vHLw3o8lNZtaKwqmSS04VmIgZ8_tNpRlX0HwYxgIW_hJY0NAeWkelP0gycct2Ppl_SZFHK_r8yHvVlH23FowdX8RgtKPQ2sqLG9qhsP3Ldx6YbVkqlvR7Y84C_Sb-5vUSljBJR8d9YhGmG-QGe38QDDWqOu1afGoj7WaEMLnBBAGvx4sbMcByTOvkn6x58XlYhZiS_WmtWlYOepYFBwnbXRLTCQuLH5F49hHHQZDn0qI-_aYZF_2U8DwNdwV1yo7E9bbfbi97i3vrOTcwJTIAQKHpBNO5OVE1yv1ZYzg7k-viiovbtFywgvU14AXtUZqgMKLAQISxyLPQQcQbm6dfcUSAnStbRgSlBAg==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering stock data retrieval**\\n\\nI need to think about retrying the process, possibly using loops to effectively gather information. Maybe the market close data from the spot will be enough, but I should check if I can use only the most recent output, which just has the latest numbers and percentage change. I also need to individually fetch quotes with retries if needed. Let’s aim for a more robust method to get the historical data as well.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"网络有点抽风，我补抓一下 603629.SH 利通电子 的K线和财务，重点看它是不是“卖飞了”，还是只是情绪加速。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eab51e5544819a859a0a6c3c936b57\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_zPtUP3GCrO56EQ5KUH1v5a0C|fc_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eab51e72c4819a9ede11ddec177b76","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nimport akshare as ak, time, json\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\ndef retry(fn, *args, **kwargs):\n    err=None\n    for i in range(5):\n        try:\n            return fn(*args, **kwargs)\n        except Exception as e:\n            err=e\n            time.sleep(1+i)\n    raise err\n\nsymbol='603629'\nres={}\n# use fast spot snapshot for latest too\nspot = retry(ak.stock_zh_a_spot)\nrow = spot[spot['代码']=='sh603629'].iloc[0]\nres['spot'] = {k:(v.item() if hasattr(v,'item') else v) for k,v in row.to_dict().items()}\n\nend=datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\nstart=(datetime.now()-timedelta(days=260)).strftime('%Y%m%d')\nh = retry(ak.stock_zh_a_hist, symbol=symbol, period='daily', start_date=start, end_date=end, adjust='qfq')\nres['last5']=h.tail(5).to_dict('records')\nlast=h.iloc[-1]\nclose=float(last['收盘'])\nres['stats']={\n 'last_date': str(last['日期']),\n 'close': close,\n 'pct_chg': float(last['涨跌幅']),\n 'ma5': round(h['收盘'].tail(5).mean(),2),\n 'ma10': round(h['收盘'].tail(10).mean(),2),\n 'ma20': round(h['收盘'].tail(20).mean(),2),\n 'ma60': round(h['收盘'].tail(60).mean(),2),\n 'high_120d': round(h['最高'].tail(120).max(),2),\n 'low_120d': round(h['最低'].tail(120).min(),2),\n 'from_120d_high_pct': round((close/h['最高'].tail(120).max()-1)*100,2),\n 'return_5d_pct': round((close/float(h.iloc[-6]['收盘'])-1)*100,2) if len(h)>6 else None,\n 'return_10d_pct': round((close/float(h.iloc[-11]['收盘'])-1)*100,2) if len(h)>11 else None,\n 'return_20d_pct': round((close/float(h.iloc[-21]['收盘'])-1)*100,2) if len(h)>21 else None,\n 'return_60d_pct': round((close/float(h.iloc[-61]['收盘'])-1)*100,2) if len(h)>61 else None,\n 'turnover': float(last['换手率']),\n 'amt_yi': round(float(last['成交额'])/1e8,2),\n}\ntry:\n    fa=retry(ak.stock_financial_abstract_ths, symbol=symbol, indicator='按报告期')\n    res['fa_tail']=fa.tail(4).to_dict('records')\nexcept Exception as e:\n    res['fa_err']=repr(e)\ntry:\n    zy=retry(ak.stock_zyjs_ths, symbol=symbol)\n    res['profile']=zy.to_dict('records')\nexcept Exception as e:\n    res['profile_err']=repr(e)\nprint(json.dumps(res, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2, default=str))\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":180},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 - <<'PY'\\nimport akshare as ak, time, json\\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\\n\\ndef retry(fn, *args, **kwargs):\\n    err=None\\n    for i in range(5):\\n        try:\\n            return fn(*args, **kwargs)\\n        except Exception as e:\\n            err=e\\n            time.sleep(1+i)\\n    raise err\\n\\nsymbol='603629'\\nres={}\\n# use fast spot snapshot for latest too\\nspot = retry(ak.stock_zh_a_spot)\\nrow = spot[spot['代码']=='sh603629'].iloc[0]\\nres['spot'] = {k:(v.item() if hasattr(v,'item') else v) for k,v in row.to_dict().items()}\\n\\nend=datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\\nstart=(datetime.now()-timedelta(days=260)).strftime('%Y%m%d')\\nh = retry(ak.stock_zh_a_hist, symbol=symbol, period='daily', start_date=start, end_date=end, adjust='qfq')\\nres['last5']=h.tail(5).to_dict('records')\\nlast=h.iloc[-1]\\nclose=float(last['收盘'])\\nres['stats']={\\n 'last_date': str(last['日期']),\\n 'close': close,\\n 'pct_chg': float(last['涨跌幅']),\\n 'ma5': round(h['收盘'].tail(5).mean(),2),\\n 'ma10': round(h['收盘'].tail(10).mean(),2),\\n 'ma20': round(h['收盘'].tail(20).mean(),2),\\n 'ma60': round(h['收盘'].tail(60).mean(),2),\\n 'high_120d': round(h['最高'].tail(120).max(),2),\\n 'low_120d': round(h['最低'].tail(120).min(),2),\\n 'from_120d_high_pct': round((close/h['最高'].tail(120).max()-1)*100,2),\\n 'return_5d_pct': round((close/float(h.iloc[-6]['收盘'])-1)*100,2) if len(h)>6 else None,\\n 'return_10d_pct': round((close/float(h.iloc[-11]['收盘'])-1)*100,2) if len(h)>11 else None,\\n 'return_20d_pct': round((close/float(h.iloc[-21]['收盘'])-1)*100,2) if len(h)>21 else None,\\n 'return_60d_pct': round((close/float(h.iloc[-61]['收盘'])-1)*100,2) if len(h)>61 else None,\\n 'turnover': float(last['换手率']),\\n 'amt_yi': round(float(last['成交额'])/1e8,2),\\n}\\ntry:\\n    fa=retry(ak.stock_financial_abstract_ths, symbol=symbol, indicator='按报告期')\\n    res['fa_tail']=fa.tail(4).to_dict('records')\\nexcept Exception as e:\\n    res['fa_err']=repr(e)\\ntry:\\n    zy=retry(ak.stock_zyjs_ths, symbol=symbol)\\n    res['profile']=zy.to_dict('records')\\nexcept Exception as e:\\n    res['profile_err']=repr(e)\\nprint(json.dumps(res, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2, default=str))\\nPY\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent\",\"timeout\":180}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":55344,"output":917,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56261,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776989463698,"responseId":"resp_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eab519791c819a9d39fcbdec1c0085"}}
