{"type":"message","id":"39494ca0","parentId":"6e702ca1","timestamp":"2026-04-24T00:18:41.361Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering growth strategies**\n\nI'm looking at a high-beta theme growth story. If someone sold after a rise or to avoid holding a high-volatility ticket, that's totally valid. It doesn't necessarily mean selling was wrong if the stock keeps rising.  \n\nIf the question is about buying back, it’s best to wait a day or two to see if it can hold above yesterday’s close of 108.2 and ideally past 110/112. I'll mention that we couldn’t fetch the full K-line due to network issues and might offer a detailed analysis later if needed.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eab6b6faa8819a9fc5303cfcce1b8a\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp6rbErj_01nXj8skAAPtyqNMFA8WTIeQn7JC4t32pBBNKVAIjOkaXiak8IaP98cKVd6By4ZlYkCNonhLUtc6AgRhSq8PK_niITnVdW6R6RR9Ik6Yp8ZtzX2LdrkACZewtmiWtcadTIwMeU9OIBBAKLjrO2UOomzxfflH5Rf3-flTRH629HfqgES1bdO4hfUAARBrhmvYI0Up2UdcBj5aJ35UDm8-bIrAmzFJfPpV6K_R7eLcrKjtNNPECHUjpwCQ73hSBF795QrzPdK2UnAfSv6nJ01cl2-wB4faLUK-xT_xWXlDauA_Q-zrLbHdotRtZtK7Cz4m78iGQTIxoojfLM300g878EWLkfsP4IS4C7rSlhtZndiVHAz03NpzhqatX5jOfyHUbw9Z9x0SYJm0dil0uOOR3PGrmBGY4R6aUbBXAsgZJQ5Ni4D7qooZK8k0zvPRx3lvVH1Iv1dCLW_Pv8Eray9LrsLt2K86SceiP8OMCHTsIuSwoasiLFEHjnWt-xWE93Hxv1DEKp3Kd3JgU8-hPNFGaajNk-1rggqduLFQUm7Bntz2kuMOukqg4cAVa2fX-GY2jHVePZTzctOt0C7msv3v4yX_JLXtdLOvU42apWTdKfvlXfxjPqEISMQrukhK9DI98eWal5Y-6cJmICbFTHqwkR3H4nYbw7JTlVSf_nIE8vlG8tk_niuqv8fFX0lfAYibd3dcw4oxK5Xk3X6MbTiBg9Vici1-NNbvhKscs46yF9wiDdNhBfLckCo0x92kc30p5rRqVupeWiasFao7Q6CDHe74hjP1LoplXABE8YbZ5QxFj3fZYhy58gvFLbS5Pc0va-DoFhalh_OZ6tXhwis5ClicC0Od4k35bpbi-Yt6fljJAMdj_eV2RZLQxdVfikFlqCFKdenNR2ASfEgHj1HE6c0ex_TT02pC9auwAsUO3-Oe4WO1c--dNqADDreftCG1OgbJav5KPFhhFw4LtrTE4h-DjlEXEKhgd2rQTcJKqms5FJRneriSrsdXqU9hcA5WgJBEQ4iwy9ZkE2SI9vZ7wIFsByj7NyzEvpqVShvsQdQc3JvS2zQrPNMm4T9ObelPpfN7-uovVWkeVTTE-hqd58H7rdG83cXjJT4nbP5X7f43tYVyog86_bg9F4O