text\":\"**Considering formatting and updates**\\n\\nI’m thinking I might need to clean up the formatting in MEMORY, like adding an extra blank line before the heading, which could look nicer. I also want to commit these changes to the main workspace. Additionally, I’m considering updating the script to stop reporting the candidate count, which seems fine to me. Giving this a little more thought, I’ll go ahead and make that commit!\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_VUzhf148fg2hwKBYcQx7vLyi|fc_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb87b2cf9c819a852112b38619a82f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"git -C /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace status --short && echo '---' && git -C /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace add MEMORY.md scripts/nightly_memory_distill.py memory/nightly_rules/2026-04-24.md memory/nightly_memory_job_state.json memory/nightly_distill/2026-04-24.md && git -C /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace commit -m \"Auto-promote nightly memory rules\"","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":60},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"git -C /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace status --short && echo '---' && git -C /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace add MEMORY.md scripts/nightly_memory_distill.py memory/nightly_rules/2026-04-24.md memory/nightly_memory_job_state.json memory/nightly_distill/2026-04-24.md && git -C /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace commit -m \\\"Auto-promote nightly memory rules\\\"\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent\",\"timeout\":60}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":139744,"output":184,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":139928,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777043369489,"responseId":"resp_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb87abb9b0819ab2ed5a75b72c60d2"}}
