*\\n\\nThe developer advises against using exec or curl for provider messaging, recommending the OpenClaw message tool instead, but cron operates outside of that runtime. I wonder if I could utilize OpenClaw CLI to spawn sessions or send messages. Looking at the documentation might help. However, a simpler solution could be writing a shell script, run_periodic_task_with_alert.sh, to execute periodic_task_executor. If it fails (nonzero), it could trigger OpenClaw to send a message, adhering to the instructions.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering task failure handling**\\n\\nI should look into editing `periodic_task_executor.py` to ensure that on failure, it invokes `openclaw sessions spawn` with parameters like runtime subagent and lightContext true. I want to avoid getting stuck in loops, especially if the original task fails. Using a message plugin or Feishu IM would be better, but it’s tricky from the script. At least sending a concise Feishu DM with the task details helps avoid infinite recursion if `openclaw` fails.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，我把“失败就飞书提醒你”这层也补上。先查一下最稳的落法，尽量不用脆弱的土办法。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb88c57f4c819ab2dc86b1c7857c95\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_hCoe7XWZqiQ3B0guCmQ9p4I8|fc_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb88c58444819aaac8f24b6e3b6537","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw help 2>/dev/null | sed -n '1,220p'","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":20},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"openclaw help 2>/dev/null | sed -n '1,220p'\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent\",\"timeout\":20}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_U3XbRf6zzabXE7q0L6gA036h|fc_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb88c58450819aacdc2808a98783f1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /Users/ling/Library/pnpm/global/5/.pnpm/openclaw@2026.4.10_*/node_modules/openclaw/docs -type f | xargs grep -nH -E 'message send|messages?\\b|notify|send a message|proactive' 2>/dev/null | head -120","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":30},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"find /Users/ling/Library/pnpm/global/5/.pnpm/openclaw@2026.4.10_*/node_modules/openclaw/docs -type f | xargs grep -nH -E 'message send|messages?\\\\b|notify|send a message|proactive' 2>/dev/null | head -120\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent\",\"timeout\":30}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dFT31fC6OkXNONpAjxZG3rsg|fc_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb88c58458819a8b7a7bf969c416b6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '1,220p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent/periodic_task_executor.py","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":20},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"sed -n '1,220p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent/periodic_task_executor.py\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent\",\"timeout\":20}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":151988,"output":1515,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":153503,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777043619577,"responseId":"resp_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb88a5fe90819aa1f9ed249da852bb"}}
