ibrary/pnpm/global/5/.pnpm/openclaw@2026.4.10_@emnapi+core@1.9.2_@emnapi+runtime@1.9.2_@napi-rs+canvas@0.1.97_@typ_a90ffd2929abe8f398b8e8e6d84b8ef0/node_modules/openclaw/docs/tools/tts.md:256:  - Resolution order: `messages.tts.providers.openai.baseUrl` -> `OPENAI_TTS_BASE_URL` -> `https://api.openai.com/v1`\n/Users/ling/Library/pnpm/global/5/.pnpm/openclaw@2026.4.10_@emnapi+core@1.9.2_@emnapi+runtime@1.9.2_@napi-rs+canvas@0.1.97_@typ_a90ffd2929abe8f398b8e8e6d84b8ef0/node_modules/openclaw/docs/tools/tts.md:285:When `messages.tts.auto` is `tagged`, these directives are required to trigger audio.\n/Users/ling/Library/pnpm/global/5/.pnpm/openclaw@2026.4.10_@emnapi+core@1.9.2_@emnapi+runtime@1.9.2_@napi-rs+canvas@0.1.97_@typ_a90ffd2929abe8f398b8e8e6d84b8ef0/node_modules/openclaw/docs/tools/tts.md:319:  messages: {\n/Users/ling/Library/pnpm/global/5/.pnpm/openclaw@2026.4.10_@emnapi+core@1.9.2_@emnapi+runtime@1.9.2_@napi-rs+canvas@0.1.97_@typ_a90ffd2929abe8f398b8e8e6d84b8ef0/node_modules/openclaw/docs/tools/tts.md:333:  messages: {\n/Users/ling/Library/pnpm/global/5/.pnpm/openclaw@2026.4.10_@emnapi+core@1.9.2_@emnapi+runtime@1.9.2_@napi-rs+canvas@0.1.97_@typ_a90ffd2929abe8f398b8e8e6d84b8ef0/node_modules/openclaw/docs/tools/tts.md:349:`messages.tts.prefsPath`).\n/Users/ling/Library/pnpm/global/5/.pnpm/openclaw@2026.4.10_@emnapi+core@1.9.2_@emnapi+runtime@1.9.2_@napi-rs+canvas@0.1.97_@typ_a90ffd2929abe8f398b8e8e6d84b8ef0/node_modules/openclaw/docs/tools/tts.md:358:These override `messages.tts.*` for that host.\n/Users/ling/Library/pnpm/global/5/.pnpm/openclaw@2026.4.10_@emnapi+core@1.9.2_@emnapi+runtime@1.9.2_@napi-rs+canvas@0.1.97_@typ_a90ffd2929abe8f398b8e8e6d84b8ef0/node_modules/openclaw/docs/tools/tts.md:362:- **Feishu / Matrix / Telegram / WhatsApp**: Opus voice message (`opus_48000_64` from ElevenLabs, `opus` from OpenAI).\n/Users/ling/Library/pnpm/global/5/.pnpm/openclaw@2026.4.10_@emnapi+core@1.9.2_@emnapi+runtime@1.9.2_@napi-rs+canvas@0.1.97_@typ_a90ffd2929abe8f398