{"type":"message","id":"14353209","parentId":"e030df8f","timestamp":"2026-04-24T15:20:08.726Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_qU8FQJydEagJdQx4myRPgk0b|fc_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8a272370819a92c587bafc3e1b5e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            \"updated\": True,\n        }\n    if \"error\" in lower or \"failed\" in lower:\n        return {\n            \"update_status\": \"error\",\n            \"recommendation\": \"⚠️ 更新失败\",\n            \"reason\": text.splitlines()[-1][:160],\n            \"updated\": False,\n        }\n    return {\n        \"update_status\": \"unknown\",\n        \"recommendation\": \"🔍 需人工确认\",\n        \"reason\": text.splitlines()[-1][:160],\n        \"updated\": False,\n    }\n\n\ndef evaluate_clawhub_skill(\n    item: dict[str, str],\n    roots: list[tuple[Path, str]],\n    auto_update_safe: bool,\n) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    name = item[\"name\"]\n    version = item[\"version\"]\n    loc = resolve_skill(name, roots)\n    if not loc:\n        return {\n            \"name\": name,\n            \"version\": version,\n            \"installed\": False,\n            \"status\": \"missing\",\n            \"recommendation\": \"⏭ 记录存在但本地缺失\",\n            \"reason\": \"clawhub list 有记录，但在实际技能目录未找到\",\n            \"source\": \"missing\",\n            \"source_label\": \"缺失\",\n        }\n\n    risk = scan_risk(loc.path)\n    origin = read_clawhub_origin(loc.path)\n    result: dict[str, Any] = {\n        \"name\": name,\n        \"version\": version,\n        \"installed\": True,\n        \"path\": str(loc.path),\n        \"source\": loc.root_kind,\n        \"source_label\": ROOT_LABELS.get(loc.root_kind, loc.root_kind),\n        \"code_count\": risk[\"code_count\"],\n        \"risk_hits\": risk[\"risk_hits\"],\n        \"clawhub_origin\": origin,\n    }\n\n    # 不是 ClawHub 托管目录，但本地可用：不能再报“未安装”\n    if loc.root_kind != \"clawhub\":\n        result.update(\n            {\n                \"status\": \"available_non_clawhub\",\n                \"recommendation\": f\"✅ 已安装（{ROOT_LABELS.get(loc.root_kind, loc.root_kind)}）\",\n                \"reason\": \"本地可用，但不在 ClawHub 托管目录；不应标记为未安装\",\n            }\n        )\n        return result\n\n    # ClawHub 托管目录\n    if risk[\"risk_hits\"]:\n        result.update(\n            {\n                \"status\": \"managed_review\",\n                \"recommendation\": \"⚠️ 需review\",\n                \"reason\": f\"检测到敏感模式：{risk['risk_hits'][0]}\",\n            }\n        )\n        return result\n\n    if auto_update_safe:\n        stdout, stderr, rc = run_cmd([\"clawhub\", \"update\", name], timeout=120, cwd=WORKSPACE)\n        parsed = parse_clawhub_update_output(name, \"\\n\".join([stdout, stderr]).strip())\n        result.update(parsed)\n        result[\"update_stdout\"] = stdout\n        result[\"update_stderr\"] = stderr\n        result[\"update_rc\"] = rc\n        result[\"status\"] = parsed[\"update_status\"]\n    else:\n        result.update(\n            {\n                \"status\": \"managed_detected\",\n                \"recommendation\": \"🔄 可自动检查\",\n                \"reason\": \"ClawHub 托管技能，可在安全模式下执行自动更新\",\n            }\n        )\n    return result\n\n\ndef check_openclaw_version() -> dict[str, Any]:\n    current_out, current_err, _ = run_cmd([\"openclaw\", \"--version\"], timeout=20)\n    latest_out, latest_err, _ = run_cmd([\"npm\", \"show\", \"openclaw\", \"version\"], timeout=30)\n    current = (current_out or current_err).strip().splitlines()[0] if (current_out or current_err).strip() else \"unknown\"\n    latest = (latest_out or latest_err).strip().splitlines()[0] if (latest_out or latest_err).strip() else \"unknown\"\n    current_version_match = re.search(r\"(\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+)\", current)\n    latest_version_match = re.search(r\"(\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+)\", latest)\n    current_version = current_version_match.group(1) if current_version_match else current\n    latest_version = latest_version_match.group(1) if latest_version_match else latest\n    needs_update = current_version != \"unknown\" and latest_version != \"unknown\" and current_version != latest_version\n    return {\n        \"current\": current_version,\n        \"latest\": latest_version,\n        \"needs_update\": needs_update,\n        \"raw_current\": current,\n        \"raw_latest\": latest,\n    }\n\n\ndef print_summary(results: list[dict[str, Any]], local_only: list[dict[str, Any]], version_info: dict[str, Any], auto_update_safe: bool) -> None:\n    updated = [r for r in results if r.get(\"status\") == \"updated\"]\n    up_to_date = [r for r in results if r.get(\"status\") == \"up_to_date\"]\n    keep_local = [r for r in results if r.get(\"status\") in {\"local_changes\", \"available_non_clawhub\"}]\n    review = [r for r in results if r.get(\"status\") in {\"managed_review\", \"suspicious\", \"error\", \"unknown\"}]\n    missing = [r for r in results if r.get(\"status\") == \"missing\"]\n\n    print(\"=\" * 72)\n    print(\"🔍 Skill / OpenClaw 更新检查 v5\")\n    print(\"=\" * 72)\n    print(f\"\\n📦 ClawHub 记录: {len(results)} 个\")\n    print(f\"📚 本地额外技能: {len(local_only)} 个\")\n    print(f\"🤖 自动更新模式: {'开启' if auto_update_safe else '关闭'}\")\n\n    print(\"\\n一、ClawHub 记录技能\")\n    print(\"┌\" + \"─\" * 70 + \"┐\")\n    print(f\"│ {'Skill':<28} {'来源':<14} {'结论':<24} │\")\n    print(\"├\" + \"─\" * 70 + \"┤\")\n    for r in results:\n        name = r[\"name\"][:28]\n        source = r.get(\"source_label\", \"-\")[:14]\n        rec = r.get(\"recommendation\", \"-\")[:24]\n        print(f\"│ {name:<28} {source:<14} {rec:<24} │\")\n    print(\"└\" + \"─\" * 70 + \"┘\")\n\n    if updated:\n        print(f\"\\n🚀 已自动更新（{len(updated)} 个）：\")\n        for r in updated:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}: {r.get('reason', '')}\")\n\n    if up_to_date:\n        print(f\"\\n✅ 已是最新（{len(up_to_date)} 个）：\")\n        print(\"  • \" + \"、\".join(r[\"name\"] for r in up_to_date))\n\n    if keep_local:\n        print(f\"\\n✅ 保留本地（{len(keep_local)} 个）：\")\n        for r in keep_local:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}: {r.get('reason', '')}\")\n\n    if review:\n        print(f\"\\n⚠️ 需 review（{len(review)} 个）：\")\n        for r in review:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}: {r.get('reason', '')}\")\n\n    if missing:\n        print(f\"\\n⏭ 记录漂移 / 缺失（{len(missing)} 个）：\")\n        for r in missing:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}: {r.get('reason', '')}\")\n\n    if local_only:\n        print(f\"\\n二、本地可用但不受 ClawHub 托管的技能（{len(local_only)} 个）\")\n        for item in local_only:\n            print(f\"  • {item['name']} [{item['source_label']}]\")\n\n    print(\"\\n三、OpenClaw 版本\")\n    if version_info.get(\"needs_update\"):\n        print(f\"  • 当前: {version_info['current']} | 最新: {version_info['latest']} | 建议升级 OpenClaw\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"  • 当前: {version_info['current']} | 最新: {version_info['latest']} | 已同步\")\n\n    print(\"\\n四、结论\")\n    if updated:\n        print(f\"  • 已自动更新 {len(updated)} 个安全技能。\")\n    else:\n        print(\"  • 本轮没有成功自动更新的技能。\")\n    print(\"  • 不再把内置 / 扩展 / 本地技能误报为“未安装”。\")\n    if missing:\n        print(\"  • 存在 clawhub 记录漂移，建议后续清理无效记录或重装缺失项。\")\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"Check skills across real roots and auto-update safe ClawHub skills\")\n    parser.add_argument(\"--auto-update-safe\", action=\"store_true\", help=\"run `clawhub update <slug>` for ClawHub-managed skills\")\n    args = parser.parse_args()\n\n    roots = iter_skill_roots()\n    clawhub_skills = get_installed_clawhub_skills()\n    clawhub_names = {item[\"name\"] for item in clawhub_skills}\n\n    results = [evaluate_clawhub_skill(item, roots, auto_update_safe=args.auto_update_safe) for item in clawhub_skills]\n    local_only = gather_local_only_skills(clawhub_names, roots)\n    version_info = check_openclaw_version()\n\n    payload = {\n        \"checked_at\": __import__(\"datetime\").datetime.now().isoformat(),\n        \"auto_update_safe\": args.auto_update_safe,\n        \"roots\": [{\"path\": str(path), \"kind\": kind, \"label\": ROOT_LABELS.get(kind, kind)} for path, kind in roots],\n        \"clawhub_results\": results,\n        \"local_only\": local_only,\n        \"openclaw\": version_info,\n    }\n    OUTPUT_JSON.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    OUTPUT_JSON.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2) + \"\\n\", encoding=\"utf-8\")\n\n    print_summary(results, local_only, version_info, args.auto_update_safe)\n    print(f\"\\n📄 已保存: {OUTPUT_JSON}\")\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777044008711}}
{"type":"message","id":"9c28fcbf","parentId":"14353209","timestamp":"2026-04-24T15:20:22.319Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Optimizing script logic**\n\nI have a script that needs optimizing based on a user's concern with local modifications. It seems the current setup causes it to show \"保留本地\" and no update suggestions. I should implement better logic to detect upstream changes even with local modifications present, producing a message like \"需合并review\" instead of \"无需更新.\" I might compare it to the latest published version and check what commands are available, possibly using the clawhub skill to read the necessary documentation.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8a34f8c0819a900cb20ce78faa77\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp64o05zkxjSbe22Ld6y1oz5l-8Q60Q7nv2RgRAE5-NzXDbsQYY430TQnKy2xmRhf_tpfWrc8G2XrBFK67hQF36n8KkPgv2tMPHUNMoCk5v5bMPxqEQ-UZPcdzKlMSXBwoYO9yKL3d6qbgR97lc_jLqa-qFVUm3nbGz3vpEXVPnLPX9OcMKSlCxvo4af4T_mS8C-Af0rzTB4JGVHG3vH7pTepP3YlRW0V6v5HBbgxPeFRYY3nqTKSdxB--OAp1XWWNHZQxNDKXT8JagewR6whO5bMKIxWlW3ZOYsPkgv5oHZwO9wHzH7dbCXlFBVGI8dJQ-7q4M4lyHtROtbukNGxTJ1FTmo6_hzCXbn-a03BiHGyrx0nenlBE6Je4X7OEjNtYVbOD5e8oIHaPaRN24F3jzWjzzRWqOp-yfWQVnnV0Nt3aUDGNdUWoR8yiOgrufPhMkaMwcj-NUTNdtg9J-I9Os1ca_acQHpYSS2h9AGaYxByZaWultWPTkK1rv0zmakcHCBnE2lsozyxtqZbsaz18NQy0-PGYax3CpIx6B-GKqx_jJ_nOPBZ8tbzIp8b5tpW8KkMzdiAWqjII2JQ6eyZo36bCI-tK7oXvfWYWmU81H0TSpdMNoffMPVctDF2vAr8cMuuzHK9CnpPiXr_SPE0SSvUj9P67ixaAaP3oUO2yf5mOB9rcPPEal7LYgQ6t9liMBxqgJYb-eGKGoyARD5TmSzO26jJ17MoZBN3o5Lu0x8ag4vU5M4WPO7NRE7lVQhFsBMjgKcbJgWcGqdtC64cvTqcLPjqVpzRsoxzbBwU9Ybj2uqtOhVHuS4voONXPDYBIdONfz2mpV_cZdppC0cY4EB6gn3IWI4pzKUUyymZnWHFu0NCDDHdkJI2LZG_TjryilqwkpfpISeU0PEsSvF8BlzRUnJznDY819Zkfeio2ads3iTgbLe2UPEYWB2ERL4ErsYv1D2ih6PcQbN-6GmVKsPe86bWI6CK73oM9uDroIz7Y2W1uDIbLlY_UFzrcc5pGsIfnbP94NSys7bficB9aO4z6OOWcN4QoVMXoquNaQEynn1U5nThsS3G1l8uLPWcYTdA70FNeizw3UEjPM9zUXWjpVOv6ANm4J7ypYgt4yjIHK1WkUgu-Ok6m3Spbtq6-YFm09rGAi9KT3vWxCB