{"type":"message","id":"1f40005e","parentId":"9c28fcbf","timestamp":"2026-04-24T15:20:22.407Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7llsuM3axutmZz3YZFnjGjrT|fc_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8a34f9fc819aa062d30243a69ab5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: clawhub\ndescription: Use the ClawHub CLI to search, install, update, and publish agent skills from clawhub.com. Use when you need to fetch new skills on the fly, sync installed skills to latest or a specific version, or publish new/updated skill folders with the npm-installed clawhub CLI.\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"node\",\n              \"kind\": \"node\",\n              \"package\": \"clawhub\",\n              \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install ClawHub CLI (npm)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# ClawHub CLI\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nnpm i -g clawhub\n```\n\nAuth (publish)\n\n```bash\nclawhub login\nclawhub whoami\n```\n\nSearch\n\n```bash\nclawhub search \"postgres backups\"\n```\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nclawhub install my-skill\nclawhub install my-skill --version 1.2.3\n```\n\nUpdate (hash-based match + upgrade)\n\n```bash\nclawhub update my-skill\nclawhub update my-skill --version 1.2.3\nclawhub update --all\nclawhub update my-skill --force\nclawhub update --all --no-input --force\n```\n\nList\n\n```bash\nclawhub list\n```\n\nPublish\n\n```bash\nclawhub publish ./my-skill --slug my-skill --name \"My Skill\" --version 1.2.0 --changelog \"Fixes + docs\"\n```\n\nNotes\n\n- Default registry: https://clawhub.com (override with CLAWHUB_REGISTRY or --registry)\n- Default workdir: cwd (falls back to OpenClaw workspace); install dir: ./skills (override with --workdir / --dir / CLAWHUB_WORKDIR)\n- Update command hashes local files, resolves matching version, and upgrades to latest unless --version is set\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777044022397}}
{"type":"message","id":"3bf91e5c","parentId":"1f40005e","timestamp":"2026-04-24T15:20:35.834Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Inspecting clawhub CLI capabilities**\n\nI think it's time to inspect the capabilities of the clawhub CLI. Maybe I could start by searching for information or looking at its help outputs. I could run commands like `clawhub --help`, `clawhub update --help`, or even `clawhub view?`. It seems important to check the output of the installed script in JSON format. So, I'll go ahead and run these commands to get more clarity on what clawhub can do!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8a421130819a9f25af415ed8f3b7\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp64pC67kuG7X25WhiMRlCSOJHiBAiijm9uIesMLGAAa_bvigNrEDBIr0FpjDqBQvTa_GAfEuwG4s1gieaP1XkZH3-Wz35OEvZyosEnc3Y8RLGKhtKZr4OctfH9uJiZZZRhC9dmwSkbhToMbStaX-y5IYGemmrlWmfoVLfY_ja30B_8IeKq_wjSP9Rdnfd8ZVmxYcmbQWPwrmyNdBZdje9BY8vxy5kmnub9HIr-MZisOVxI2w_eVY5AM77JFZrFXbHtpHT0S8du7wY7q-mA5cWeUTAnNwKmkVjUm50IU5e1WeBLaMX849rVXY3rGxKZjBhdNJGcR4O58Ku6YMXwMWJUM7O4PjMeiKl_6LdeTRL8Ulb2fqbjSTaWICHhlUm5oKhgnOIZi5c5lnGYdEeGlgBvNcNGxnbBuCizfkkLw066mWGvno0N0GAZBhHFJENrpKXmBEJmKVIsTL3I7ZqUCl8dzoQ8P0VwQ-mtd5Omd0F1mAJSvKPdSGO4V-8V7hwahi2YlRdRUlyVXOzcZe-r1_UdUfteNAVN8Tp3pFPhC-vfVdGQI0hgFR0P10Q6ktIanFabHOBJo38xj7WDjwGasQIL3FTbNE5FtwqRcYDk-IfCr0qVEx0oQAil2x1i1Stdm12wBTQOzdyJhHlNgukuGRGXzG4zLYSNi0C42ylOcbE_fOFyykm_Zndv3cTkPfj1EUuaR5kgCj85sPGcfdt6iuMuIOFzjp61h9__Xxze6eFwCwd9ckvXwZbf0q3x9v62H2HsSPCOuk4E_xE8kUKpHFFG5rFV7P3ZHTobn0BspuNorMKl5Ke8YOHK12UadWlBV5CjXqnwXGe2TkkbSXXxFlibNeh9ehOcW_fDtf_8MBGCY8EhU9zeljs9Egj9Sdvb3ovUlRIMXIE9m3ngi9JX4bx1PkZfzq7gLP1onxYGamh6klOvc8pukvBRdOuz5twkoNJKWCcCmeQEdL1VRlE_QhM_MOZFdSGJI6nSJBIqF3H3HbwfUbQe_cC8TUc3YGdePczqdUd2bPNI-Ph1vjTB1zYBn-xLCoieHlf-is_s8xyKgWYDjZBVZQlyconcyBAKfu70MhuMjDmGhHYbODFsMG66M-m0Gr5qsC5IJVOIEBfj2z_XodNZWGY7AC5x6fn5zswJsNDcpyfDEWt_H8Ag-7jcyMlPY5NkTnp7whkga5SNvvmck0=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Inspecting clawhub CLI capabilities**\\n\\nI think it's time to inspect the capabilities of the clawhub CLI. Maybe I could start by searching for information or looking at its help outputs. I could run commands like `clawhub --help`, `clawhub update --help`, or even `clawhub view?`. It seems important to check the output of the installed script in JSON format. So, I'll go ahead and run these commands to get more clarity on what clawhub can do!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"我已经定位到症结了：  \n**现在脚本把“本地 hash 不匹配”直接当成“保留本地”结束了，没继续判断“上游其实有没有新版本”。**  \n这就会把“已本地化但上游有重要更新”的技能，一律归到“不用更新”。这确实把更新检查做废了。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8a4213d8819a844c16615da9fdcb\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_zlHH4FR19VtYwTbitIGWl1sg|fc_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8a4218a4819abf223c2fc1a3b1fa","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub --help | sed -n '1,220p'","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":30},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"clawhub --help | sed -n '1,220p'\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent\",\"timeout\":30}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_IPu06SRzNBgma053l6l6Qe6x|fc_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8a4218b4819a952ecca62509238c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub update --help | sed -n '1,220p'","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":30},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"clawhub update --help | sed -n '1,220p'\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent\",\"timeout\":30}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_N0wh7wJPKivKHpnsJryfsPtv|fc_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8a4218bc819aa894c58efa54c35c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill_update_check.py --auto-update-safe | sed -n '1,220p'","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":120},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill_update_check.py --auto-update-safe | sed -n '1,220p'\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent\",\"timeout\":120}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":203013,"output":327,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":203340,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777044022410,"responseId":"resp_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8a390e84819aa2ecda2e1b25b95c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"96ac4eaf","parentId":"3bf91e5c","timestamp":"2026-04-24T15:20:36.346Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_zlHH4FR19VtYwTbitIGWl1sg|fc_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8a4218a4819abf223c2fc1a3b1fa","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Usage: clawhub [options] [command]\n\nClawHub CLI v0.7.0 (097c98ea)\ninstall, update, search, and publish agent skills.\n\nOptions:\n  -V, --cli-version                       Show CLI version\n  --workdir <dir>                         Working directory (default: cwd)\n  --dir <dir>                             Skills directory (relative to workdir, default: skills)\n  --site <url>                            Site base URL (for browser login)\n  --registry <url>                        Registry API base URL\n  --no-input                              Disable prompts\n  -h, --help                              display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  login [options]                         Log in (opens browser or stores token)\n  logout                                  Remove stored token\n  whoami                                  Validate token\n  auth                                    Authentication commands\n  search [options] <query...>             Vector search skills\n  install [options] <slug>                Install into <dir>/<slug>\n  update [options] [slug]                 Update installed skills\n  uninstall [options] <slug>              Uninstall a skill\n  list                                    List installed skills (from lockfile)\n  explore [options]                       Browse latest updated skills from the registry\n  inspect [options] <slug>                Fetch skill metadata and files without installing\n  publish [options] <path>                Publish skill from folder\n  delete [options] <slug>                 Soft-delete a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  hide [options] <slug>                   Hide a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  undelete [options] <slug>               Restore a hidden skill (moderator/admin only)\n  unhide [options] <slug>                 Unhide a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  ban-user [options] <handleOrId>         Ban a user and delete owned skills (moderator/admin only)\n  set-role [options] <handleOrId> <role>  Change a user role (admin only)\n  star [options] <slug>                   Add a skill to your highlights\n  unstar [options] <slug>                 Remove a skill from your highlights\n  sync [options]                          Scan local skills and publish new/updated ones\n\nEnv:\n  CLAWHUB_SITE\n  CLAWHUB_REGISTRY\n  CLAWHUB_WORKDIR\n  (CLAWDHUB_* supported)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":414,"aggregated":"Usage: clawhub [options] [command]\n\nClawHub CLI v0.7.0 (097c98ea)\ninstall, update, search, and publish agent skills.\n\nOptions:\n  -V, --cli-version                       Show CLI version\n  --workdir <dir>                         Working directory (default: cwd)\n  --dir <dir>                             Skills directory (relative to workdir, default: skills)\n  --site <url>                            Site base URL (for browser login)\n  --registry <url>                        Registry API base URL\n  --no-input                              Disable prompts\n  -h, --help                              display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  login [options]                         Log in (opens browser or stores token)\n  logout                                  Remove stored token\n  whoami                                  Validate token\n  auth                                    Authentication commands\n  search [options] <query...>             Vector search skills\n  install [options] <slug>                Install into <dir>/<slug>\n  update [options] [slug]                 Update installed skills\n  uninstall [options] <slug>              Uninstall a skill\n  list                                    List installed skills (from lockfile)\n  explore [options]                       Browse latest updated skills from the registry\n  inspect [options] <slug>                Fetch skill metadata and files without installing\n  publish [options] <path>                Publish skill from folder\n  delete [options] <slug>                 Soft-delete a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  hide [options] <slug>                   Hide a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  undelete [options] <slug>               Restore a hidden skill (moderator/admin only)\n  unhide [options] <slug>                 Unhide a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  ban-user [options] <handleOrId>         Ban a user and delete owned skills (moderator/admin only)\n  set-role [options] <handleOrId> <role>  Change a user role (admin only)\n  star [options] <slug>                   Add a skill to your highlights\n  unstar [options] <slug>                 Remove a skill from your highlights\n  sync [options]                          Scan local skills and publish new/updated ones\n\nEnv:\n  CLAWHUB_SITE\n  CLAWHUB_REGISTRY\n  CLAWHUB_WORKDIR\n  (CLAWDHUB_* supported)","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777044036336}}
{"type":"message","id":"b1317f9b","parentId":"96ac4eaf","timestamp":"2026-04-24T15:20:36.357Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_IPu06SRzNBgma053l6l6Qe6x|fc_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8a4218b4819a952ecca62509238c","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Usage: clawhub update [options] [slug]\n\nUpdate installed skills\n\nArguments:\n  slug                 Skill slug\n\nOptions:\n  --all                Update all installed skills\n  --version <version>  Update to specific version (single slug only)\n  --force              Overwrite when local files do not match any version\n  -h, --help           display help for command"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":413,"aggregated":"Usage: clawhub update [options] [slug]\n\nUpdate installed skills\n\nArguments:\n  slug                 Skill slug\n\nOptions:\n  --all                Update all installed skills\n  --version <version>  Update to specific version (single slug only)\n  --force              Overwrite when local files do not match any version\n  -h, --help           display help for command","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777044036346}}
