{"type":"message","id":"661c4633","parentId":"99a5f5db","timestamp":"2026-04-24T15:25:59.081Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Summarizing repository updates**\n\nI need to provide a concise summary of what changed and the observed examples. So, I might mention that the memory search function is unavailable, but it's not vital right now since the focus is on current issues. I can suggest that we do a repo update checker with automatic labels like \"可快进/需rebase/需人工合并.\" The user has asked for optimization, so I’ll mention that I fixed skills and maybe propose refining classifications next. Notable updates include: multi-search-engine and openclaw-spirits now flagged for merge review.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8b8598a4819aa0a6b5b70a749d90\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp64uFrSzReDmsPKoUuNk7rZ8ViX7k5-p-GVxAJOGMvwWkWsq3ankk0EbEhBnTAdm8CTyJYxzWRYlxV3OTR7tsGA-btaN327OzcOKSxXUyKIXV0IFQ2CTVPQSizIZOk_xHhkHtSzZ4AcGAsRcDc9tr8VfrH0wH_FjBilz3fczUKW_swc93Re7Hqe6ls3nUalPcnPm7yWFXtZSPrAB2Ys5SUnRKcvKUYXfdgJmHCjjvW0NtnR9STDrXNwMizOAwYnW4mNS_grmh6Gx3jk1u4nWwjMsy4eNREJKUyWPQxBkb0rPUYWODBSiMc12zN5LGuAAK7PddG1SqT9hUGhm607uZo155LBHVjciHyF0ik2xMCooUzqB_-dkx6siYQOBqzwQ5rX33E9VPLQNgqlTAo6ShV8MuQyLaoGyrnQrElRZoWh_NmNySAZ6mubVVbdIyX2rjU8pTldEX-GSt2bdcOJ_YIqOeQz4lVVCNTOYqrEXxBPFebKTHDbjPm7qU-15HKRIe4k5cxyV7tJzE7Uky-fwOk9fLWYooKevIfuyECuPDKpw9zCMfr9xiLO8tPIbXKwiMCyCxmSZ-bR3YVKiMyH28lkdReSPg41UsoNDL47as_2C4Cycbeep06gRjRMWEms2ZS5Jrsnh5hn2fSoasZL2WdkCmir9cB1Vh3ZjEhVCteNXDIUQC9Fb4XMj3bE8hLarRRmpvxtpfrv_Q4VPMC43AsE8zOD6iCnnyl6iqlY4PZ4NbXUnOFSsKY3qRtQZgEysHo7mOak92uReyECt6FGFIVrWCzndDD8sR_8kmWbLmowQtB6SkoMYfMY1gH4zC_mawgtmsx-dpIzrbkikGmYc-j9WfR1C8yFCzvmcmXHuXWFa2uSKxnh6PtE4szPG3iqqEHJssb5DLcpkfGWSkGslbm2fjuGia3DaWjysIgRj0vGCoSqtGETcOAvahDQfcrlKYG8ufKKOk5nHejvJYNhRWT6nxI85ephXGkVGiTdt-N6p8PL1Vf-NDLjBuSCAtpdZfx6hchkbQbKt9ofAhWd1lAg7CAu0IRFNLFRx4oWp1pvtDW3hP2d0YCWxrQ_ttZYaZRRKCgQQQfgxO1lc0DYnSZ6RFyMcvRAg-L8EBrrFox_XAL4YfEYcLN1Z0zvp9sch12enKnQw7CkF0obrnDaa6OVBbxmea4bP_yyFSzxQCvPpNsh5hR5PHqGdIFLAk6RgqXWyblrjZd9mknhkSLTfjXj4yAyYqfhXBpjWa5vZ8xtq45DGZc0cXSDrzzM4oReEGYwTiZXYe3MODNDaU_TzYXVNDAKaPsqKf_HdwDBncjjkE7kBK5H_A7Dljqz5cg8Q8YcTeTdTHbGM2fzH4JbgCjmaIQtGDDDGp6yS3QvHzOyFETOAkUFFBOkdDx8S3vABCujyZJd8gnd_8JTWRH14vS2-XX1-QnqTruveJMY5s0Rc-3CmbtZAdfjXx9Q4uOK7zr9hdjY6Y3s8mzCaW1wVeIuzAL-Gih7xk2MBsRUQMBcw1jb0hF-EKEbgCSyWAwas47bDv4asNyS1nT-5Fu48ct_eggk4bteSO9H4qQduhwYkSY9y4qi-_FsddyATToEE1yQIPD3qUjhHWM35s3bwBXXh7QJk5kPxmKkBqgnMqPKlZxavIrgMXWbjKY-PUpa4rWtikyZXRF6wiuonVxhL2nUL117Z5aU2KvCiUY3kUFex8sj80enErh1Hnit8SRbxv1iX5pASsETEZwJp3EG4QcA_e4lCWnLYUU9ZWPiyp-aVJcTWotcFsWl5ugZwd5KVpvITlavdouQdFaLQEp5Sgg8HkrbDKzYS_Vi1CjiQIikbxpsn_VHmLCNOCgrQlAt9nBanOWuvlHgizdeKXa9uqcu56ZqO3LjVUrDeghUKeg_J0tCNgWH2ZnmBwNEX0rdwBjqu9m_qnbWsNEEQH_Crqie7SZ6lrm0JtJo9TEjD5m-KnQ5PsJOVIYtzIK4SPsW3oc1s8plq7ntiyEdHAIZpkuoJKZ0bYG610z4saNeKKe0UTBWm1jeKfNt5nVeEXq024Qt624offgUGO-hTXRvVNhhlRYa28l0MSqZtiWcMPa13LrONWUpPBRlIWa4zL89vKu0Tr\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Summarizing repository updates**\\n\\nI need to provide a concise summary of what changed and the observed examples. So, I might mention that the memory search function is unavailable, but it's not vital right now since the focus is on current issues. I can suggest that we do a repo update checker with automatic labels like \\\"可快进/需rebase/需人工合并.\\\" The user has asked for optimization, so I’ll mention that I fixed skills and maybe propose refining classifications next. Notable updates include: multi-search-engine and openclaw-spirits now flagged for merge review.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]你这条反馈是对的，我已经把 **skill 更新检查** 这块修了，而且现在不再会把“本地化改造”直接等同于“无需更新”。\n\n### 这次我改了什么\n我改的是：\n- `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill_update_check.py`\n\n核心改动：\n\n1. **即使本地 hash 不匹配，也继续去查上游最新版本**\n2. 不再简单输出：\n   - `✅ 保留本地`\n3. 而是分成两类：\n   - **本地已改造，但上游没新版本** → `✅ 保留本地`\n   - **本地已改造，且上游有新版本** → `🧩 需合并上游`\n\n### 现在实际跑出来的结果\n我已经重跑了一遍，新的结果里已经抓到两个典型例子：\n\n#### 本地已改造，但上游有新版本\n- **multi-search-engine**：`2.0.1 → 2.1.3`\n- **openclaw-spirits**：`1.2.3 → 1.3.2`\n\n它们现在不再被错误归类成“保留本地”，而是明确标成：\n\n- **🧩 需合并上游**\n\n#### 本地已改造，但上游没变\n比如这些就会继续留在：\n- `✅ 保留本地`\n\n因为确实没有新的上游版本值得合并。\n\n---\n\n### 这次修复的意义\n之前的逻辑其实是：\n\n> 本地改过 → update 跳过 → 报“保留本地” → 更新检查失真\n\n现在变成：\n\n> 本地改过 → 继续探测上游版本 →  \n> 有新版就提示“要合并” → 没新版才说“保留本地”\n\n这才有检查更新的意义。\n\n---\n\n### 我已经提交了\n- **commit**: `278c5ff85` — `Detect upstream updates for localized skills`\n\n---\n\n### 现在的判断\n- **skill 更新检查**：这次已经修到位了，至少核心失真点已经补上\n- **仓库更新检查**：我看了现有报告，问题没 skill 这边这么严重，它本来就会写：\n  - `behind / ahead`\n  - `与上游已分叉，应先评估再合并`\n  \n所以眼下最该修的，确实就是这条 skill 更新判断，我已经修掉了。\n\n### 下一步我建议\n我可以继续把 repo 更新检查也再往前推一步，做成更实用的四档：\n\n1. **可直接快进**\n2. **可自动 rebase**\n3. **本地有改动但上游有更新，需合并**\n4. **高风险分叉，人工处理**\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步就直接把 **仓库更新检查** 也改成这个口径。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8b859a44819aa0092e92e3b2a857\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":23587,"output":846,"cacheRead":203904,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":228337,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777044335040,"responseId":"resp_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8b715c80819a89eb66fd1d091293"}}
