{"type":"message","id":"8f328bbf","parentId":"3bb1d694","timestamp":"2026-04-24T15:31:11.519Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_uHEichvQB0kigm8e373NND0T|fc_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8cb1a2b8819aa1cddc44feeef5bd","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# GitHub 仓库更新报告 — 2026-04-24\n\n**检查仓库数：5** | 上游待更新：3 | 本地有变化：5 | 已同步：0\n\n### 🔔 主仓上游待更新\n\n#### RD-Agent ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐\n- 当前版本：697ade1 | 上游版本：26560b3\n- behind 991 | ahead 1 | 工作区：干净\n- **更新判断：值得关注但不建议直接更新：与上游已分叉（behind 991 / ahead 1），应先评估再合并**\n\n**上游主要变更：**\n- 🟡 Bug修复 `26560b3` fix: preserve null end_time when rendering dataset segments template (#1326)\n- 🟡 Bug修复 `f8aeea0` fix: prevent calendar index overflow when signal data ends early (#1324)\n- 🔵 重构 `a74712c` refactor: unify qlib experiment configs, runners, and templates (#1320)\n- ⚪ 其他 `ce8d6a7` fix(collect_info): parse package names safely from requirements constraints (#1313)\n- ⚪ 维护 `5a6346a` docs: add documentation for Data Science configurable options (#1301)\n\n#### quant_system ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐\n- 当前版本：447c490 | 上游版本：v3.12.0-51-g4254672\n- behind 552 | ahead 1 | 工作区：untracked 9\n- **更新判断：值得关注但不建议直接更新：与上游已分叉（behind 552 / ahead 1），应先评估再合并**\n\n**上游主要变更：**\n- ⚪ 其他 `4254672` merge: update daily_stock_analysis with upstream v3.13.0\n- ⚪ 其他 `dbdf30d` fix(ci): avoid secrets in docker publish step conditions\n- ⚪ 其他 `a585565` chore(release): consolidate docker publish workflows and fix desktop log encoding\n- 📝 文档 `7cf3a88` docs: update CHANGELOG for v3.13.0 release\n- 🔵 重构 `303a50d` refactor: 补充一份最小化文档说明，明确 Docker 安装场景下应以 Git tag/镜像 tag 判断版本… (#1091) (#1093)\n\n#### ai-hedge-fund ⭐⭐⭐⭐\n- 当前版本：419c10f | 上游版本：0f6ac48\n- behind 15 | ahead 0 | 工作区：untracked 1\n- **更新判断：值得更新：落后 15 个 commits，建议一次性合并**\n\n**上游主要变更：**\n- ⚪ 其他 `0f6ac48` Create initial data layer\n- ⚪ 其他 `578fdc9` Add Opus 4.7\n- ⚪ 其他 `7ee6450` Add volume\n- ⚪ 其他 `f411d37` Add test_client.py\n- ⚪ 其他 `cf2aa11` Add API client to v2\n\n### 🛠️ 主仓本地有变化\n\n#### daily_stock_analysis\n- behind 0 | ahead 16 | 工作区：untracked 33\n- 本地未推送提交：\n  - ⚪ 其他 `4254672` merge: update daily_stock_analysis with upstream v3.13.0\n  - ⚪ 其他 `36cb1f4` Merge upstream main: review fixes + LiteLLM streaming + /v1/models support\n  - ⚪ 其他 `67d7eb3` Merge remote-tracking branch 'upstream/main'\n  - ⚪ 其他 `7ebf0fd` Merge upstream/main\n  - ⚪ 其他 `af89112` merge: update daily_stock_analysis with upstream/main\n\n#### TrendRadar\n- behind 0 | ahead 1 | 工作区：staged 1 / modified 2 / untracked 39\n- 本地未推送提交：\n  - ⚪ 其他 `c8577a8` Hide internal count lines from Feishu report\n\n#### quant_system\n- behind 552 | ahead 1 | 工作区：untracked 9\n- 本地未推送提交：\n  - ⚪ 其他 `447c490` initial: 小市值量化策略回测系统\n\n#### RD-Agent\n- behind 991 | ahead 1 | 工作区：干净\n- 本地未推送提交：\n  - ⚪ 其他 `697ade1` Initial clone via GitHub API\n\n#### ai-hedge-fund\n- behind 15 | ahead 0 | 工作区：untracked 1\n\n\n## ⚪ 扩展仓（1仓）\n\n检查仓库数：1 | 上游待更新：0 | 本地有变化：0 | 已同步：1\n\n### ✅ 扩展仓已同步（1）\nfile-organizer\n\n\n---\n*由 github-repo-monitor 自动生成 | 09:00*"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777044671504}}
{"type":"message","id":"43db863a","parentId":"8f328bbf","timestamp":"2026-04-24T15:32:38.781Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Improving report generation**\n\nI’m focusing on implementing an improved report using state JSON. Maybe I should create a script in the workspace to render the classification or directly edit the latest markdown. Running a utility script could generate a better report now. I wonder if searching for \"github-repo-monitor\" provides useful script names? I'll be creating or modifying a script to read the latest state JSON by date and write to the latest markdown file without causing interference.\n\n**Classifying results for reports**\n\nIf I can’t find the generator, maybe creating a post-processor as a wrapper will suffice. Since the user indicated \"好\", there’s no rush to fully automate the report tonight, but it's still a good idea to get started. I need to check the structure of the state JSON to classify results. I’ll categorize them based on conditions like errors, sync status, and how to handle clean-up actions. The user wanted four classification types, focusing on sync conditions and variations in ahead/behind status.\n\n**Defining report classifications**\n\nI’m looking at the classifications for handling repository updates. The second type is an automatic rebase for clean states when both ahead and behind are less than or equal to 20. The third type focuses on local changes with upstream updates needing a merge. Finally, the fourth type flags high-risk situations like fetch errors or breaking changes. I think I should implement a new script to read the state JSON and generate an improved report, maybe adding an action_class field in the refined JSON.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8cfbbc7c819ab9be7e73b504e7ef\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp64z7j9a1MAK15qBnGVr6-fY12_H4uRRkdxc6_yIzp9Hyz_ZI7F04FDbw_c_ZOyHxwugzv94SUPJ66x2MJ0BMmGFvjU5yndOS7lk3