7R76zDjWoxSQfLgbe_HH4mXe1FR8EeXbu2o4z0NqNpeZujD9TSFfcRD5rUdV3rXR\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Improving report generation**\\n\\nI’m focusing on implementing an improved report using state JSON. Maybe I should create a script in the workspace to render the classification or directly edit the latest markdown. Running a utility script could generate a better report now. I wonder if searching for \\\"github-repo-monitor\\\" provides useful script names? I'll be creating or modifying a script to read the latest state JSON by date and write to the latest markdown file without causing interference.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Classifying results for reports**\\n\\nIf I can’t find the generator, maybe creating a post-processor as a wrapper will suffice. Since the user indicated \\\"好\\\", there’s no rush to fully automate the report tonight, but it's still a good idea to get started. I need to check the structure of the state JSON to classify results. I’ll categorize them based on conditions like errors, sync status, and how to handle clean-up actions. The user wanted four classification types, focusing on sync conditions and variations in ahead/behind status.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Defining report classifications**\\n\\nI’m looking at the classifications for handling repository updates. The second type is an automatic rebase for clean states when both ahead and behind are less than or equal to 20. The third type focuses on local changes with upstream updates needing a merge. Finally, the fourth type flags high-risk situations like fetch errors or breaking changes. I think I should implement a new script to read the state JSON and generate an improved report, maybe adding an action_class field in the refined JSON.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"我先直接把“动作分级器”落成脚本，并基于今晚最新状态生成一版新报告。  \n这样今晚你就能看到新口径，不用等旧监控脚本慢慢重构。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8cfbbef0819ab1f7123344204f7b\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_WFTVn8eSLFxxSgMb48vly3iD|fc_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8cfbc384819a98387ce55f8fc114","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/refine_github_repo_update_report.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nREPORTS_DIR = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports')\nLATEST_STATE = REPORTS_DIR / 'github_repo_update_state_20260424.json'\nLATEST_MD = REPORTS_DIR / 'github_repo_update_latest.md'\nLATEST_JSON = REPORTS_DIR / 'github_repo_update_action_latest.json'\n\n\ndef load_state(path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    return json.loads(path.read_text(encoding='utf-8'))\n\n\ndef worktree_text(item: dict[str, Any]) -> str:\n    if not item.get('working_tree_dirty'):\n        return '干净'\n    parts = []\n    if item.get('staged_count'):\n        parts.append(f\"staged {item['staged_count']}\")\n    if item.get('modified_count'):\n        parts.append(f\"modified {item['modified_count']}\")\n    if item.get('untracked_count'):\n        parts.append(f\"untracked {item['untracked_count']}\")\n    return ' / '.join(parts) if parts else 'dirty'\n\n\ndef classify(item: dict[str, Any]) -> tuple[str, str, str]:\n    behind = int(item.get('commits_behind') or 0)\n    ahead = int(item.get('commits_ahead') or 0)\n    dirty = bool(item.get('working_tree_dirty'))\n    breaking = bool(item.get('breaking_changes'))\n    fetch_error = item.get('fetch_error')\n\n    if fetch_error:\n        return 'manual_high_risk', '🔴 高风险人工处理', f'抓取上游失败：{fetch_error}'\n    if breaking:\n        return 'manual_high_risk', '🔴 高风险人工处理', '检测到 breaking changes，不应自动推进'\n    if behind == 0 and ahead == 0 and not dirty:\n        return 'synced', '✅ 已同步', '本地与上游一致'\n    if behind > 0 and ahead == 0 and not dirty:\n        if behind <= 20:\n            return 'fast_forward', '🟢 可直接快进', f'仅落后 {behind} 个提交，且工作区干净，可直接 fast-forward'\n        return 'manual_high_risk', '🔴 高风险人工处理', f'落后 {behind} 个提交，跨度过大，建议人工评估后再合并'\n    if behind > 0 and ahead > 0 and not dirty:\n        if behind <= 20 and ahead <= 20:\n            return 'auto_rebase', '🔵 可自动 rebase', f'本地 ahead {ahead} / upstream behind {behind}，且工作区干净，可自动 rebase 评估'\n        return 'needs_merge', '🟠 本地有改动且上游有更新，需合并', f'已分叉（behind {behind} / ahead {ahead}），应保留本地改动并合并上游'\n    if behind > 0 and (ahead > 0 or dirty):\n        return 'needs_merge', '🟠 本地有改动且上游有更新，需合并', f'本地有改动（ahead {ahead}，工作区 {worktree_text(item)}）且上游还有 {behind} 个提交未并入'\n    if dirty and behind == 0:\n        return 'local_only', '🟡 仅本地待整理', f'上游无新提交，但本地工作区有改动：{worktree_text(item)}'\n    if ahead > 0 and behind == 0:\n        return 'local_only', '🟡 仅本地待整理', f'本地有 {ahead} 个未推送提交，上游无新增'\n    return 'manual_review', '⚠️ 需人工 review', '状态复杂，需人工判断'\n\n\ndef format_commit_lines(commits: list[dict[str, Any]], limit: int = 5) -> list[str]:\n    lines = []\n    for commit in commits[:limit]:\n        priority = commit.get('priority', '⚪ 其他')\n        short = commit.get('short', '???????')\n        msg = commit.get('message', '').strip()\n        lines.append(f\"- {priority} `{short}` {msg}\")\n    return lines\n\n\ndef build_report(state: dict[str, Any]) -> tuple[str, dict[str, Any]]:\n    checked_at = state.get('checked_at', '')\n    results = state.get('results', [])\n    enriched = []\n    buckets = {\n        'fast_forward': [],\n        'auto_rebase': [],\n        'needs_merge': [],\n        'manual_high_risk': [],\n        'local_only': [],\n        'synced': [],\n        'manual_review': [],\n    }\n    for item in results:\n        action_key, action_label, action_reason = classify(item)\n        row = dict(item)\n        row['action_key'] = action_key\n        row['action_label'] = action_label\n        row['action_reason'] = action_reason\n        row['worktree_text'] = worktree_text(item)\n        enriched.append(row)\n        buckets.setdefault(action_key, []).append(row)\n\n    date_label = checked_at[:10] if checked_at else datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d')\n    total = len(results)\n    actionable = len(buckets['fast_forward']) + len(buckets['auto_rebase']) + len(buckets['needs_merge']) + len(buckets['manual_high_risk'])\n    md = [f\"# GitHub 仓库更新报告 — {date_label}\", '']\n    md.append(f\"**检查仓库数：{total}** | 可直接推进：{len(buckets['fast_forward']) + len(buckets['auto_rebase'])} | 需合并：{len(buckets['needs_merge'])} | 高风险：{len(buckets['manual_high_risk'])}\")\n    md.append('')\n\n    sections = [\n        ('🟢 可直接快进', 'fast_forward'),\n        ('🔵 可自动 rebase', 'auto_rebase'),\n        ('🟠 本地有改动且上游有更新，需合并', 'needs_merge'),\n        ('🔴 高风险人工处理', 'manual_high_risk'),\n        ('🟡 仅本地待整理', 'local_only'),\n    ]\n\n    for title, key in sections:\n        items = buckets.get(key, [])\n        md.append(f\"## {title}（{len(items)}）\")\n        md.append('')\n        if not items:\n            md.append('- 无')\n            md.append('')\n            continue\n        for item in items:\n            md.append(f\"### {item['name']}\")\n            md.append(f\"- 当前版本：{item.get('local_tag', item.get('local_sha', '-'))} | 上游版本：{item.get('upstream_tag', item.get('upstream_sha', '-'))}\")\n            md.append(f\"- behind {item.get('commits_behind', 0)} | ahead {item.get('commits_ahead', 0)} | 工作区：{item['worktree_text']}\")\n            md.append(f\"- **动作判断：{item['action_reason']}**\")\n            if item.get('new_commits'):\n                md.append('- 上游主要变更：')\n                md.extend(format_commit_lines(item['new_commits']))\n            if item.get('local_commits') and key in {'auto_rebase', 'needs_merge', 'local_only'}:\n                md.append('- 本地提交：')\n                md.extend(format_commit_lines(item['local_commits']))\n            md.append('')\n\n    md.append('## ✅ 已同步')\n    md.append('')\n    if buckets['synced']:\n        md.append('- ' + '、'.join(item['name'] for item in buckets['synced']))\n    else:\n        md.append('- 无')\n    md.append('')\n    md.append('---')\n    md.append('*由 refine_github_repo_update_report 自动生成*')\n\n    summary = {\n        'checked_at': checked_at,\n        'counts': {key: len(value) for key, value in buckets.items()},\n        'results': enriched,\n        'actionable_count': actionable,\n    }\n    return '\\n'.join(md).rstrip() + '\\n', summary\n\n\ndef main() -> int:\n    state_path = LATEST_STATE\n    if not state_path.exists():\n        candidates = sorted(REPORTS_DIR.glob('github_repo_update_state_*.json'))\n        if not candidates:\n            raise SystemExit('no github_repo_update_state json found')\n        state_path = candidates[-1]\n    state = load_state(state_path)\n    md, summary = build_report(state)\n    date_label = (state.get('checked_at') or '')[:10].replace('-', '') or datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\n    dated_md = REPORTS_DIR / f'github_repo_update_report_{date_label}.md'\n    dated_json = REPORTS_DIR / f'github_repo_update_action_{date_label}.json'\n    LATEST_MD.write_text(md, encoding='utf-8')\n    dated_md.write_text(md, encoding='utf-8')\n    LATEST_JSON.write_text(json.dumps(summary, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2) + '\\n', encoding='utf-8')\n    dated_json.write_text(json.dumps(summary, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2) + '\\n', encoding='utf-8')\n    print(json.dumps({'state': str(state_path), 'latest_md': str(LATEST_MD), 'dated_md': str(dated_md), 'latest_json': str(LATEST_JSON), 'dated_json': str(dated_json), 'counts': summary['counts']}, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n    return 0\n\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    raise SystemExit(main())\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/refine_github_repo_update_report.py\",\"content\":\"#!/usr/bin/env python3\\nfrom __future__ import annotations\\n\\nimport json\\nfrom datetime import datetime\\nfrom pathlib import Path\\nfrom typing import Any\\n\\nREPORTS_DIR = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports')\\nLATEST_STATE = REPORTS_DIR / 'github_repo_update_state_20260424.json'\\nLATEST_MD = REPORTS_DIR / 'github_repo_update_latest.md'\\nLATEST_JSON = REPORTS_DIR / 'github_repo_update_action_latest.json'\\n\\n\\ndef load_state(path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\\n    return json.loads(path.read_text(encoding='utf-8'))\\n\\n\\ndef worktree_text(item: dict[str, Any]) -> str:\\n    if not item.get('working_tree_dirty'):\\n        return '干净'\\n    parts = []\\n    if item.get('staged_count'):\\n        parts.append(f\\\"staged {item['staged_count']}\\\")\\n    if item.get('modified_count'):\\n        parts.append(f\\\"modified {item['modified_count']}\\\")\\n    if item.get('untracked_count'):\\n        parts.append(f\\\"untracked {item['untracked_count']}\\\")\\n    return ' / '.join(parts) if parts else 'dirty'\\n\\n\\ndef classify(item: dict[str, Any]) -> tuple[str, str, str]:\\n    behind = int(item.get('commits_behind') or 0)\\n    ahead = int(item.get('commits_ahead') or 0)\\n    dirty = bool(item.get('working_tree_dirty'))\\n    breaking = bool(item.get('breaking_changes'))\\n    fetch_error = item.get('fetch_error')\\n\\n    if fetch_error:\\n        return 'manual_high_risk', '🔴 高风险人工处理', f'抓取上游失败：{fetch_error}'\\n    if breaking:\\n        return 'manual_high_risk', '🔴 高风险人工处理', '检测到 breaking changes，不应自动推进'\\n    if behind == 0 and ahead == 0 and not dirty:\\n        return 'synced', '✅ 已同步', '本地与上游一致'\\n    if behind > 0 and ahead == 0 and not dirty:\\n        if behind <= 20:\\n            return 'fast_forward', '🟢 可直接快进', f'仅落后 {behind} 个提交，且工作区干净，可直接 fast-forward'\\n        return 'manual_high_risk', '🔴 高风险人工处理', f'落后 {behind} 个提交，跨度过大，建议人工评估后再合并'\\n    if behind > 0 and ahead > 0 and not dirty:\\n        if behind <= 20 and ahead <= 20:\\n            return 'auto_rebase', '🔵 可自动 rebase', f'本地 ahead {ahead} / upstream behind {behind}，且工作区干净，可自动 rebase 评估'\\n        return 'needs_merge', '🟠 本地有改动且上游有更新，需合并', f'已分叉（behind {behind} / ahead {ahead}），应保留本地改动并合并上游'\\n    if behind > 0 and (ahead > 0 or dirty):\\n        return 'needs_merge', '🟠 本地有改动且上游有更新，需合并', f'本地有改动（ahead {ahead}，工作区 {worktree_text(item)}）且上游还有 {behind} 个提交未并入'\\n    if dirty and behind == 0:\\n        return 'local_only', '🟡 仅本地待整理', f'上游无新提交，但本地工作区有改动：{worktree_text(item)}'\\n    if ahead > 0 and behind == 0:\\n        return 'local_only', '🟡 仅本地待整理', f'本地有 {ahead} 个未推送提交，上游无新增'\\n    return 'manual_review', '⚠️ 需人工 review', '状态复杂，需人工判断'\\n\\n\\ndef format_commit_lines(commits: list[dict[str, Any]], limit: int = 5) -> list[str]:\\n    lines = []\\n    for commit in commits[:limit]:\\n        priority = commit.get('priority', '⚪ 其他')\\n        short = commit.get('short', '???????')\\n        msg = commit.get('message', '').strip()\\n        lines.append(f\\\"- {priority} `{short}` {msg}\\\")\\n    return lines\\n\\n\\ndef build_report(state: dict[str, Any]) -> tuple[str, dict[str, Any]]:\\n    checked_at = state.get('checked_at', '')\\n    results = state.get('results', [])\\n    enriched = []\\n    buckets = {\\n        'fast_forward': [],\\n        'auto_rebase': [],\\n        'needs_merge': [],\\n        'manual_high_risk': [],\\n        'local_only': [],\\n        'synced': [],\\n        'manual_review': [],\\n    }\\n    for item in results:\\n        action_key, action_label, action_reason = classify(item)\\n        row = dict(item)\\n        row['action_key'] = action_key\\n        row['action_label'] = action_label\\n        row['action_reason'] = action_reason\\n        row['worktree_text'] = worktree_text(item)\\n        enriched.append(row)\\n        buckets.setdefault(action_key, []).append(row)\\n\\n    date_label = checked_at[:10] if checked_at else datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d')\\n    total = len(results)\\n    actionable = len(buckets['fast_forward']) + len(buckets['auto_rebase']) + len(buckets['needs_merge']) + len(buckets['manual_high_risk'])\\n    md = [f\\\"# GitHub 仓库更新报告 — {date_label}\\\", '']\\n    md.append(f\\\"**检查仓库数：{total}** | 可直接推进：{len(buckets['fast_forward']) + len(buckets['auto_rebase'])} | 需合并：{len(buckets['needs_merge'])} | 高风险：{len(buckets['manual_high_risk'])}\\\")\\n    md.append('')\\n\\n    sections = [\\n        ('🟢 可直接快进', 'fast_forward'),\\n        ('🔵 可自动 rebase', 'auto_rebase'),\\n        ('🟠 本地有改动且上游有更新，需合并', 'needs_merge'),\\n        ('🔴 高风险人工处理', 'manual_high_risk'),\\n        ('🟡 仅本地待整理', 'local_only'),\\n    ]\\n\\n    for title, key in sections:\\n        items = buckets.get(key, [])\\n        md.append(f\\\"## {title}（{len(items)}）\\\")\\n        md.append('')\\n        if not items:\\n            md.append('- 无')\\n            md.append('')\\n            continue\\n        for item in items:\\n            md.append(f\\\"### {item['name']}\\\")\\n            md.append(f\\\"- 当前版本：{item.get('local_tag', item.get('local_sha', '-'))} | 上游版本：{item.get('upstream_tag', item.get('upstream_sha', '-'))}\\\")\\n            md.append(f\\\"- behind {item.get('commits_behind', 0)} | ahead {item.get('commits_ahead', 0)} | 工作区：{item['worktree_text']}\\\")\\n            md.append(f\\\"- **动作判断：{item['action_reason']}**\\\")\\n            if item.get('new_commits'):\\n                md.append('- 上游主要变更：')\\n                md.extend(format_commit_lines(item['new_commits']))\\n            if item.get('local_commits') and key in {'auto_rebase', 'needs_merge', 'local_only'}:\\n                md.append('- 本地提交：')\\n                md.extend(format_commit_lines(item['local_commits']))\\n            md.append('')\\n\\n    md.append('## ✅ 已同步')\\n    md.append('')\\n    if buckets['synced']:\\n        md.append('- ' + '、'.join(item['name'] for item in buckets['synced']))\\n    else:\\n        md.append('- 无')\\n    md.append('')\\n    md.append('---')\\n    md.append('*由 refine_github_repo_update_report 自动生成*')\\n\\n    summary = {\\n        'checked_at': checked_at,\\n        'counts': {key: len(value) for key, value in buckets.items()},\\n        'results': enriched,\\n        'actionable_count': actionable,\\n    }\\n    return '\\\\n'.join(md).rstrip() + '\\\\n', summary\\n\\n\\ndef main() -> int:\\n    state_path = LATEST_STATE\\n    if not state_path.exists():\\n        candidates = sorted(REPORTS_DIR.glob('github_repo_update_state_*.json'))\\n        if not candidates:\\n            raise SystemExit('no github_repo_update_state json found')\\n        state_path = candidates[-1]\\n    state = load_state(state_path)\\n    md, summary = build_report(state)\\n    date_label = (state.get('checked_at') or '')[:10].replace('-', '') or datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\\n    dated_md = REPORTS_DIR / f'github_repo_update_report_{date_label}.md'\\n    dated_json = REPORTS_DIR / f'github_repo_update_action_{date_label}.json'\\n    LATEST_MD.write_text(md, encoding='utf-8')\\n    dated_md.write_text(md, encoding='utf-8')\\n    LATEST_JSON.write_text(json.dumps(summary, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2) + '\\\\n', encoding='utf-8')\\n    dated_json.write_text(json.dumps(summary, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2) + '\\\\n', encoding='utf-8')\\n    print(json.dumps({'state': str(state_path), 'latest_md': str(LATEST_MD), 'dated_md': str(dated_md), 'latest_json': str(LATEST_JSON), 'dated_json': str(dated_json), 'counts': summary['counts']}, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\\n    return 0\\n\\n\\nif __name__ == '__main__':\\n    raise SystemExit(main())\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"beecode","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":97070,"output":2939,"cacheRead":151808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":251817,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777044671522,"responseId":"resp_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8cc27b7c819aaafdd954d978ba91"}}
