y want to move forward, and it's clear I need to refine the `refine_github_repo_update_report.py` file. Let’s dig into the latest report and start building this policy.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Deciding update policies**\\n\\nI need to establish some reasonable update policies. For example, if a repo is clean without any ahead or dirty commits, we can consider it safe for auto-update. If the repo has a small lead or lag but is still clean, auto-updating with a backup might be appropriate. However, if it requires merging or has a high risk, it should never auto-update, and manual merges are necessary. If it's local-only and synced, no action is needed. The user seems interested in which repos fall into these categories.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Clarifying tool usage**\\n\\nI’m considering whether I should only commit a targeted file. I might mention that memory search is unavailable since the user asked about previous information, but that might not be necessary. The system mentioned that I should focus on current work, so maybe I shouldn’t use memory. The user requested \\\"点头\\\" after my proposed next step, so no memory is needed. I’ll keep my progress update brief before acting on the actual tool calls.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，我直接把这一步也落地：  \n**以后不只给“是否值得更新”，还顺手产出“自动执行清单”**，把仓库分成：\n\n- 可自动更新\n- 先备份再更新\n- 永远不自动碰，只保留本地线/人工合并\n- 无需动作","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8e3151f4819abb581b59dc6eb1b4\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_kojEia6i52WGdaH9KSnp3UA9|fc_0059dd7f9d4e6a410169eb8e3161dc819abca1bb87b3d0a21c","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/refine_github_repo_update_report.py","edits":[{"oldText":"LATEST_MD = REPORTS_DIR / 'github_repo_update_latest.md'\nLATEST_JSON = REPORTS_DIR / 'github_repo_update_action_latest.json'\n","newText":"LATEST_MD = REPORTS_DIR / 'github_repo_update_latest.md'\nLATEST_JSON = REPORTS_DIR / 'github_repo_update_action_latest.json'\nLATEST_PLAN_MD = REPORTS_DIR / 'github_repo_update_execution_latest.md'\nLATEST_PLAN_JSON = REPORTS_DIR / 'github_repo_update_execution_latest.json'\n"},{"oldText":"def build_report(state: dict[str, Any]) -> tuple[str, dict[str, Any]]:\n","newText":"def build_execution_policy(item: dict[str, Any]) -> tuple[str, str]:\n    action_key = item.get('action_key')\n    if action_key == 'fast_forward':\n        return 'auto_update', '可自动更新'\n    if action_key == 'auto_rebase':\n        return 'backup_then_update', '先备份再更新'\n    if action_key in {'needs_merge', 'manual_high_risk', 'manual_review'}:\n        return 'keep_local_manual', '永远不自动碰（保留本地线/人工合并）'\n    return 'no_action', '无需动作'\n\n\ndef build_report(state: dict[str, Any]) -> tuple[str, dict[str, Any], str, dict[str, Any]]:\n"},{"oldText":"        row['final_verdict'] = final_verdict\n        row['action_reason'] = action_reason\n        row['worktree_text'] = worktree_text(item)\n","newText":"        row['final_verdict'] = final_verdict\n        row['action_reason'] = action_reason\n        row['worktree_text'] = worktree_text(item)\n        policy_key, policy_label = build_execution_policy(row)\n        row['execution_policy'] = policy_key\n        row['execution_policy_label'] = policy_label\n"},{"oldText":"    summary = {\n        'checked_at': checked_at,\n        'counts': {key: len(value) for key, value in buckets.items()},\n        'results': enriched,\n        'actionable_count': actionable,\n    }\n    return '\\n'.join(md).rstrip() + '\\n', summary\n","newText":"    execution_buckets = {\n        'auto_update': [item for item in enriched if item.get('execution_policy') == 'auto_update'],\n        'backup_then_update': [item for item in enriched if item.get('execution_policy') == 'backup_then_update'],\n        'keep_local_manual': [item for item in enriched if item.get('execution_policy') == 'keep_local_manual'],\n        'no_action': [item for item in enriched if item.get('execution_policy') == 'no_action'],\n    }\n\n    plan_md = [f\"# GitHub 仓库自动执行清单 — {date_label}\", '']\n    plan_md.append(f\"**自动更新：{len(execution_buckets['auto_update'])}** | **备份后更新：{len(execution_buckets['backup_then_update'])}** | **不自动碰：{len(execution_buckets['keep_local_manual'])}** | **无需动作：{len(execution_buckets['no_action'])}\")\n    plan_md.append('')\n    plan_sections = [\n        ('🟢 可自动更新', 'auto_update'),\n        ('🔵 先备份再更新', 'backup_then_update'),\n        ('🟠 永远不自动碰（保留本地线/人工合并）', 'keep_local_manual'),\n        ('⚪ 无需动作', 'no_action'),\n    ]\n    for title, key in plan_sections:\n        items = execution_buckets[key]\n        plan_md.append(f\"## {title}（{len(items)}）\")\n        plan_md.append('')\n        if not items:\n            plan_md.append('- 无')\n            plan_md.append('')\n            continue\n        for item in items:\n            plan_md.append(f\"### {item['name']}\")\n            plan_md.append(f\"- 最终结论：{item['final_verdict']}\")\n            plan_md.append(f\"- 执行策略：{item['execution_policy_label']}\")\n            plan_md.append(f\"- 原因：{item['action_reason']}\")\n            plan_md.append('')\n\n    summary = {\n        'checked_at': checked_at,\n        'counts': {key: len(value) for key, value in buckets.items()},\n        'results': enriched,\n        'actionable_count': actionable,\n    }\n    plan_summary = {\n        'checked_at': checked_at,\n        'counts': {key: len(value) for key, value in execution_buckets.items()},\n        'results': enriched,\n    }\n    return '\\n'.join(md).rstrip() + '\\n', summary, '\\n'.join(plan_md).rstrip() + '\\n', plan_summary\n"},{"oldText":"    md, summary = build_report(state)\n","newText":"    md, summary, plan_md, plan_summary = build_report(state)\n"},{"oldText":"    LATEST_MD.write_text(md, encoding='utf-8')\n    dated_md.write_text(md, encoding='utf-8')\n    LATEST_JSON.write_text(json.dumps(summary, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2) + '\\n', encoding='utf-8')\n    dated_json.